high_descs: Turn around and walk forward to face the knife on the counter.
Pick up the knife on the counter.
Take a step to the left to face the sink.
Wash the knife in the sink and remove it.
Turn around and cross the room and turn left to face the kitchen table.
Place the knife on the kitchen table.
anns.task_desc: To wash an knife and place it on the kitchen table.

high_descs: Turn right and walk forward, then turn right again and walk over to the counter.
Pick up the metal butter knife off of the counter.
Turn left and walk over to the sink.
Put the butter knife in the sink then turn on the water, after a couple seconds turn the water off and remove the now clean butter knife.
Turn right and walk towards the wall, then hang a right and walk over to the round white table in the corner of the room.
Put the clean butter knife on the round white table.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean butter knife on a round white table.

high_descs: Turn around and go to the counter.
Pick up the knife on the counter.
Turn left and go to the sink.
Rinse the knife off in the sink and pick it back up.
Turn around and go to the round white table.
Put the knife on the table to the left of the tomato.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean knife on the table.
